The Stunning 2018 Volkswagen Arteon R-Line.

A new era of Volkswagen luxury is here. With cutting-edge technology and state-of the-art driving assistance systems, the Arteon truly is a car like no other. Bold and original, it is designed for an individual equally as unique.

Aerodynamic contours, frameless windows and a striking overall design, the Arteon's allure endures far beyond the first encounter. Both elegant and dynamic the new four-door coupe offers a remarkable amount of space and comfort.

Beneath the bonnet of the new Arteon is the 206kW/350Nm 2.0-litre turbocharged four-cylinder engine. The 4MOTION all-wheel drive system with a seven-speed DSG dual clutch automatic transmission boasts a 0-100km/h sprint time of 5.6 seconds.
